com.compendium.core.datamodel
Class MediaIndex

java.lang.Object
  com.compendium.core.datamodel.PCObject
      com.compendium.core.datamodel.MediaIndex
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPCObject, ICoreConstants, java.io.Serializable
public class MediaIndex
extends PCObject
implements java.io.Serializable

The MediaIndex object defines the media timestamp offset of a node in a view in a specific meeting. This is used to tie a Compendium map into a video taken during a meeting.
